    <!-- Help dialog -->
    <string name="help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="help_content"><![CDATA[
<b>Quick start (USB - recommended)</b><br/>
1. Connect your tablet to the PC with a USB cable.<br/>
2. Run <b>START.bat</b> on the PC and choose <b>USB</b>.<br/>
3. In this app, keep IP as <b>127.0.0.1</b> and tap <b>Connect</b>.<br/><br/>

<b>Quick start (Wi-Fi)</b><br/>
1. Connect PC and tablet to the same Wi-Fi.<br/>
2. Run <b>START.bat</b> and choose <b>Wi-Fi</b>.<br/>
3. Enter your PC IP in this app and tap <b>Connect</b>.<br/><br/>

<b>Mode</b><br/>
• <b>Mirror</b>: clone your main monitor.<br/>
• <b>Extended</b>: use tablet as a second monitor.<br/><br/>

<b>Target monitor</b><br/>
Leave empty for automatic selection.<br/>
If needed, type monitor number (0, 1, 2...).<br/><br/>

<b>Language</b><br/>
Use the <b>EN/ES</b> button in the top bar to change all app language.<br/><br/>

<b>Stop session</b><br/>
Tap <b>Disconnect</b> in the app, or run <b>scripts\\STOP.bat</b> on PC.
    ]]></string>

